[Educator] Try meal prepping at home to have healthy options ready, like salads, sandwiches, or wraps.
[Patient] How can I make sure I'm not overeating on a limited budget?
[Educator] Pay attention to portion sizes, listen to your body's hunger cues, and avoid eating out of boredom.
[Patient] Are there any resources in my neighborhood that can help me access affordable healthy foods?
[Educator] Look into local food banks, community programs, or government assistance like SNAP for food support.
